<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.1">
<l>tavaḷavi ḷampiṟai tuḷḷumunnīrt taṇmalart teṉṟalō ṭaṉṟiloṉṟit</l>
<l>tuvaḷaveṉ ṉeñcakañ cōravīruñ cūḻpaṉi nāḷtuyi lātiruppēṉ</l>
<l>ivaḷumōr peṇkoṭi yeṉṟiraṅkā reṉṉala maintumuṉ koṇṭupōṉa</l>
<l>kuvaḷaima larniṟa vaṇṇarmaṉṉu kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The young, white crescent, the rolling three-watered [sea],</l>
<l rend="indent">with the south wind through the flowers, and the black ibis, [all] as one</l>
<l>Torment [me] so that my heart trembles [and] falters; I am sleepless</l>
<l rend="indent">until the dawn enveloped in dew.</l>
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi where dwells</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who did not pity me realizing, “She’s just a creeper[-like] girl,”</l>
<l>The one the hue of the blue lily blossom who,</l>
<l rend="indent">once robbing [me] of my five [senses] and virtue, left.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
